{"tid":1212464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵太古站乘客充電器冒煙起火　一度要疏散乘客","createTime":"2019-06-12T18:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T19:12:24.000Z","uid":92859,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7369706c5c3b0492b44be15ab414553f954b2f43","tid":1212464,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:51:50.000Z","msg":"港鐵太古站乘客充電器冒煙起火　一度要疏散乘客<br />\n 2018/11/09  <br />\n<br />\n港鐵港島綫一列列車，早上8時駛至太古站時，有乘客的外置充電器著火冒煙，乘客要疏散，消防到場時，火勢已熄滅。<br />\n<br />\n警方在早上8時許接報，一列港鐵列車內有乘客的物品冒煙起火，到達太古站月台時，發現一名乘客的外置充電器冒煙，已經熄滅，警方及消防在現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好心啲人咪係淘寶買尿袋啦，出事架嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffe0094b81deaf6edbf254a93bc57d4c8b1a850","tid":1212464,"uid":22894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:59:59.000Z","msg":"呢個係來自一班鐵膠嘅呼籲<br />\n尿袋著火的話請善用附近既滅火筒<br />\n<br />\n搭車要摸清楚緊急設備 免得出起事來累人累己<br />\n拿 唔係緊急唔好用呀 一個唔該半個鐘都無車到<br />\n影響大家翻工就麻鳩煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHPEtk5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHPEtk5.png&h=e0650ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zs39Qzu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZs39Qzu.png&h=3d5a172e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNetmF8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNetmF8.png&h=6a8ffb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0qwjsM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0qwjsM.png&h=ddd4ac0a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90M7Cew.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90M7Cew.png&h=40abe25d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<i